location.fullValue: The Rittiman Plan, New Homes At Belle Oaks

data.description: Move-in ready! 4 bed/3 bath single story home in Ventana neighborhood. Spacious open living and dining area with high ceilings, abundant natural light, and plantation shutters. Kitchen offers rich Espresso cabinetry, gas cooking, SS appliances, breakfast bar with rustic wood accent. Primary bedroom features large walk-in tile shower, double vanity, and walk-in closet. Generously sized secondary bedrooms with plantation shutters. Game room, or optional flex space is ideal for home office, gym, or extra living area. Neutral color palette throughout and tile in all wet/high traffic areas. Lounge under shade of the screened-in covered patio overlooking the private backyard and views of the greenspace. Short walk to the community pool and amenities. Short drive to shopping and dining as you are centrally located between Boerne and Bulverde.
